that their profession

00:04:32.832 --> 00:04:37.283
is this terrifying, death-defying
you know, high-wire act.

00:04:37.307 --> 00:04:39.333
Have you ever given a performance

00:04:39.357 --> 00:04:41.667
before a group of people
who have been drinking?

00:04:42.155 --> 00:04:43.799
They are putty in your hands.

00:04:43.823 --> 00:04:45.355
(Laughter)

